headline: General Motors' China Q4 Sales Rise 41% Q/Q on Strong NEV Deliveries
summary: GM and its joint ventures sell 600,000 units in the fourth quarter, up 40.6% quarter over quarter, driven by strong performance in the NEV sector.

headline: GM, TWG Motorsports launch new company for Cadillac’s F1 venture
summary: The new firm will develop powertrains for the Cadillac Formula 1 team, which is due to join the grid in 2026.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell GM and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
